This paper is about automatic query expansion (AQE) techniques, which are commonly used in information retrieval (IR) systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR. The paper also discusses distribution-based and association-based methods, which are relevant to natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) fields. Hence, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DL are also possible categories.
